Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.25,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Odds or evens...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.50,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with evens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.01,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Odds...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.19,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.68,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.66,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.36,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of the Harusame's 4th Squad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.36,0:02:09.97,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,was once considered a lone \Nflower in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:14.04,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,but after losing out \Nin a grab for power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.07,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,she stole money from the \Ngroup and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:20.11,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected her \Nto come back like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.88,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:25.20,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you to be a \Nsucker for a vixen like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.55,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Kids wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.56,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,We live in an age where everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:32.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,fits in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.17,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,But you want a woman who \Nisn't so easy to hold on to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:36.20,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Like a DS?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.22,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,She's more like a Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.72,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.22,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder it was so hard to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.51,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about your \Nbeloved Genesis here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.83,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like she couldn't \Nfit in down there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.02,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,She gambled and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.44,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,And so did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.27,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.19,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.47,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like a certain stupid captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.88,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,I don't let my emotions \Nget in the way of my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:01.65,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.79,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, she changed her face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.22,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,and name when she escaped to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.61,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,How was I supposed to recognize her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.58,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.01,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm a Nintendo fan, not a Sega fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.57,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.96,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.37,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I was interested in seeing the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.13,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,exalted team work of the Shinra,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.55,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,but they were just a bunch of grunts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.55,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who stood no chance \None-on-one against a Yato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.33,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't be much of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.74,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, they stole my glory again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.73,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,We should go show our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.28,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,To the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:46.83,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Odds or Evens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.95,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke Takasugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.64,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.30,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,He signed a pact with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.05,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,He's the leader of the mercenary \Ngroup known as the Kiheitai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.05,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Are they from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.05,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,They're samurai, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.87,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,The remnants of those savages
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.77,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who resisted until the very end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.68,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,when we opened up their land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.22,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Assho--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.28,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Admiral Abo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:15.31,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be very special for \Nyou to remember his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.30,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,He only cooperates with us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.04,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when our interests happen to coincide,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.95,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,but he can be very useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:26.35,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You could consider them the \NHarusame's enforcers on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:30.70,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,They were responsible for \Nhunting down that vixen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.96,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.96,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is one \Nissue that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.38,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that they are actually
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.24,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,a terrorist group which seeks to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,unseat the government of Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.24,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,But when we struck a deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.97,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with the central ward which
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.21,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,allowed us to sneak into Edo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.95,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,they offered to draw the \Ngovernment's trained dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:50.97,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.18,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.35,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:01.28,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Each side is using the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.60,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,so they're using the Harusame
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.55,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,to get close to the Bakufu and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.99,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,take down the central ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.85,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.92,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.40,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,They're plotting terrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.71,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I knew all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.00,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,S-So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:18.75,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.84,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,We finally obtained the right to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.17,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,strip Earth of its valuable resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.27,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,If they succeed, we'll lose \Nall our business there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.14,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I doubt that Takasugi person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.40,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,stands a chance against \Nthe Tendo or the elders,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.89,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,but he can probably crush our forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:41.52,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I-If that happens, the \Nelders will have my hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.81,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.31,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do the best you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.88,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.63,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.57,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I summoned you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.42,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,For a free meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.00,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:59.75,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,The 7th Squad is responsible \Nfor cleaning up our messes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.50,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.88,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Dispose of the tools \Nthat we no longer need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.24,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.14,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Strong words, coming from a \Ntool that never had any use but as a decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.65,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,This place would be much more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.14,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,comfortable if we disposed of that pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.08,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you both four-legged creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.65,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you get along, Captain Koro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.03,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.54,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,You have the backing of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.67,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the captains of the twelve squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.20,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to throw our support
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.99,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,behind you at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:37.27,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Asshole is just \Na puppet for the elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.86,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,All he cares about is his own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:44.13,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna work for someone \Nwho will let me run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:48.46,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you take control, Koro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.83,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.26,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to go crazy \Nand not have to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.78,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like our boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:57.65,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I have an eyepatch over one eye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.40,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,and a hook instead of a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.95,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not captain material.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.09,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the spitting \Nimage of a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.04,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,You're clearly gunning \Nto be the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:09.01,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm willing to lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.76,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna take down that \NTakasugi fool, count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.32,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.92,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found myself another samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.41,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Abuto, isolate Takasugi \Nfrom his minions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.29,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Take the fleet and wipe out his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.74,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Koro, you're \Nfree to help out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.71,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:32.97,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I won't let \Nanyone ruin my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.81,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.24,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dark everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:47.32,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Can't tell if we're moving \Nforward or backward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:52.07,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shinsuke, are we \Nmoving forward right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.18,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about sounding so whiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.83,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,I've been getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.47,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter which way we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,If you get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.83,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,just follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:08.72,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you're deep underground \Nor far above the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.59,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to take you to our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.51,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.41,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.86,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.60,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,I...  I'll follow you to hell and back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.70,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,We share the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.98,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Let us march on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Now sign this petition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.62,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,We oppose the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:33.25,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Ordinance Regarding \Nthe Healthy Development of Youths!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.90,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Before you try to regulate free speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.90,0:08:36.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,you should learn to \Nregulate your own heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.05,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Pedophilia predates manga and anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not our goal to foster \Na culture of acceptance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.08,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, I'm not a \Npedophile.  I'm a feminist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.76,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Bansai-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.02,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Lord Shinsuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.67,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,He stayed behind on the mothership
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.81,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,because the admiral needed \Nhim for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.97,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to return \Nto Edo without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.51,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Needed him for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.52,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't the slightest idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.46,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.90,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a mistake to join \Nforces with the Harusame?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.30,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.43,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,We will defeat the Bakufu \Nand rebuild the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.41,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you agree to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.39,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,But we're out of our league...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:26.30,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,The Kiheitai aren't \Non the same level as a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.38,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,galactic crime syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.82,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough, we'll become their pawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.05,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,The way things stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.15,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we've sunken to the level of the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.93,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Amanto-ass-kissing Bakufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.00,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, now that the \NBakufu and Harusame
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,are working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:45.43,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,we've become a liability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.44,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,What if Lord Shinsuke is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.58,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, you're \Nworried about Shinsuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.30,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.96,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,That man won't fall \Nbefore the Bakufu does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.85,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget the promise he made?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.29,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll simply destroy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.79,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,...the Greater Edo Ordinance Regarding \Nthe Healthy Development of Youths!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.82,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess up my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.64,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.71,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll destroy you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.23,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Master Bansai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.72,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Harusame fleet ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.98,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do they truly \Nintend to eliminate us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.62,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lord Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.38,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.31,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,So we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.39,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about cutting \Nstraight to the chase,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:33.12,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,but either way, you're going to \Nbe surprised when I say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.69,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Please die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:37.52,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not much of a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:40.70,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,It was obvious from the \Nmoment I first saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.29,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,You're sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.08,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I've been dying \Nto fight a samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.46,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,from the moment I first saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.68,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,And you kind of smell the same
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.09,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,as that other samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.57,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:58.08,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to kill \Nthat stupid samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.59,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with the silver hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.60,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,You must have super powers or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.57,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a secret behind \Nthat left eye of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.33,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:15.02,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.32,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:23.53,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:27.41,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui, we're here to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.75,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss a message or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.86,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever mentioned that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.76,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,we were up against such a big family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.51,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You Yato are too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.51,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,A blade that's too sharp will \Nattract many foes, Kamui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.49,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,You got me good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.86,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Never expected Admiral Asshole \Nto pull a fast one on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.72,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill that idiot for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:55.03,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,So feel free to rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.11,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.96,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Harusame fleet \Nbehind the Kiheitai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.50,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's Captain Koro's 8th Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.08,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,along with the admiral's personal fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.29,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we were tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.01,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.58,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,The Harusame are fighting each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:26.37,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.39,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.52,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Takechi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.24,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Harusame's 7th Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.41,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Harusame force, drawn from
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.56,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the elite ranks of the \NYato, the warrior tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:40.03,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,Their leader, the brilliant Lord Kamui,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:44.36,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,is more highly regarded \Nthan the admiral now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.16,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,The 12 squad captains are looking \Nto overthrow the admiral
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:50.08,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,and name Lord Kamui as their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.78,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,So by that reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.45,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,that fool of an admiral
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.91,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,intends to eliminate the 7th Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:59.09,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,which threatens his position?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.14,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:06.35,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,We were used as bait to isolate \Nand crush the 7th Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.06,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,So we're being used \Nby the Harusame again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:15.37,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier for us to take advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.00,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,of that useless admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.00,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.57,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying your own fangs to \Nhold onto your position...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.83,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,There are always more fools
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,when an organization begins to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.17,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Friend Takasugi, that \Nwas an excellent job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.50,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,There are no longer any \Nrogue elements to oppose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.46,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You also performed admirably, Koro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.05,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,No, Admiral Assho...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.77,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Abo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.22,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,I was simply performing \Nmy duty as one of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the 12 squad captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:49.06,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Kamui has been \Nmade an example of,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:51.66,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,the captains who supported \NKamui will come
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.43,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to their senses and swear fealty to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.44,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind of a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:57.98,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.61,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,That kid took enough poison to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.32,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,instantly leave an \Nelephant incapacitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.94,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,but he was able to fend off my blade
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.45,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,while smiling the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.56,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,And he managed to kill off
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.60,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,twenty or so of your men, \Ndespite his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.91,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that his absence
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.79,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,will be far more damaging
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.46,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,than what he did to your men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.97,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.34,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Your Kiheitai can fill the \Nvoid he's left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.59,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.00,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to be the head of \Na cat than the tail of a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.68,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be a bandit chief \Nthan a pirate or bigwig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:41.98,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm not giving \Nup the Kiheitai name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.05,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to compensate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.48,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.49,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep it simple, just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.48,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:55.49,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,He's harder to read than Kamui was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.30,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.00,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,No more fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:06.13,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Odds or evens, odds or evens...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.51,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.69,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.08,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Evens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:17.02,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, now it's your turn to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.59,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,That gambler's cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:22.02,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, you run out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.52,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I lost, so I know what \NI'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:30.03,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from a monster who \Ndoesn't die when killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.99,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,They patched me up and spared my life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:37.12,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,so I could be executed in \Nfront of the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.28,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,When's the big day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.54,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,In three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.01,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:43.54,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one of us will die first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.98,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've figured it out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:50.55,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,The people here only \Ncare about themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.77,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter how hard you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.80,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just abuse you \Nas much as they can
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.29,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,before they get rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.51,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.54,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I would prefer to be used by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:03.43,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who isn't so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:09.76,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Those sharp fangs of yours \Nwill only rot in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.95,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.88,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:23.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Searching for a place to \Nuse my sharpened fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:28.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,But this leaky boat \Nwon't take me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:33.94,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather hitch a ride on your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:38.47,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, space fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:43.20,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how the admiral \Ntook out the 7th Squad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.36,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Did he have help from the elders?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:49.29,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, I heard that the idea came \Nfrom Takasugi of the Kiheitai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.18,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:54.56,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys worked their \Nasses off for the Harusame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:58.25,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's doing jack for \Nthe sake of the Harusame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:01.22,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,If someone is in the \Nway, you eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.33,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it goes in the Harusame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.33,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Men, take a long, hard look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.36,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens to \Nthose who defy my authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.66,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,When you cross me, you cross the elders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.09,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,When you cross the elders, \Nyou cross the Harusame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.61,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,When there is no order,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.90,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a battle-hardened army will \Nbe reduced to a headless mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.60,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,How can he say that crap \Nwith a straight face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:27.35,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui, do you have any last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.75,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Can I say something real quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.02,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.86,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.86,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Kill him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.93,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Admiral Assho--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.76,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Abo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.61,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Will you allow me to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.29,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:46.95,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I never had the \Nchance to fight him one-on-one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.29,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,but I can at least serve \Nas the executioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.80,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,On my signal, jump Takasugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:18:01.36,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Our luck ran out when I \Ngot on this leaky boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:06.31,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that we share \Nthe same fight, Earth fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.84,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.32,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that neither of us \Nwill be doing any sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.94,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Sure we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.36,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Down in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.32,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.30,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice nap in hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.09,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,leaky boat crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.61,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.71,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.86,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,That gambler's cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.32,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see which one \Nof us would die first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.12,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,but you're trying to \Nget us killed together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.87,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,It's more fun to dance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:08.12,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with a batshit crazy idiot \Nthan a plain old idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.88,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai are a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.37,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.53,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing more than tools \Nthat are no longer needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.88,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you into spacedust!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:22.89,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.69,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.05,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the executioner here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:31.40,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,the only executioner \Nneeded in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.21,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Off with your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.21,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Shinsuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:45.16,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the Joi do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.08,Main01,Matako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you to hell and back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.99,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.66,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,You believe that we stand a \Nchance against the Harusame?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.39,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,We should be focusing our resources
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.46,Main01,Takechi,0000,0000,0000,,on the Greater Edo Ordinance Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.80,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.34,Main01,Bansai,0000,0000,0000,,...to pick a fight with \Nthe rest of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.35,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed monkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.55,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.05,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:09.48,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.95,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:16.39,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,I rowed out here because I was worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:18.77,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,but you're looking better than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.11,Main01,Abuto,0000,0000,0000,,Blockhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:21.61,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,The 7th Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.46,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.11,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.62,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:26.60,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.49,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the 7th Squad is back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:31.72,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,the other squads are beginning \Nto side with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.04,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The tables have been reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:34.63,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.13,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.59,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,C-Curse you, Kamui, Takasugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.49,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.55,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,A-Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.24,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running away by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.55,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you, Admiral Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.14,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You finally said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:50.08,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,I kept pretending that I didn't hear \Nyou, but you finally said it to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.77,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.05,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Get this ship moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.31,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.36,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.82,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,My men always do the work, \Nso I have no idea what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.36,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a hook on your hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.53,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.98,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be an admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:02.42,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.12,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:03.90,Main01,Koro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.59,Main01,Aho,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.37,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Kamui, Admiral Asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.65,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.79,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Admiral Nincompoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.92,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.59,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:25.51,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have to put off \Nour fight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.43,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm looking forward \Nto touring hell with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.43,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:35.41,Main01,Kamui,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing the planet of samurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:41.90,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Odds or evens, odds or evens...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.45,Main01,Takasugi,0000,0000,0000,,Evens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.20,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.84,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Odds...
