Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.53,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember a damn thing \Nabout the factory tour.
